    <h1>HTML Hyperlinks</h1>

    <p>This is an example of a link that opens in the same window:</p>
    <a href="https://www.example.com">Visit Example</a>

    <p>This is an example of a link that opens in a new window:</p>
    <a href="https://www.example.com" target="_blank">Visit Example in New Window</a>

